  "detailed_description": "This is a personal project I've been working on by myself for a while. It's a VR Action Shooter that makes you feel like Neo from the matrix.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nA mysterious group of rogues calling themselves STAR have kidnapped you. In this VR shooter you will right the wrongs of the \"evil\" Space Trading Association as you are tasked/forced into suicidal missions.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nA short concise adventure and a first glimpse into the STA Universe.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nDodge bullets and use an arsenal of weapons including a two handed assault rifle and a grenade launcher to dispense justice on those your master determines to be evil.",
  "about_the_game": "This is a personal project I've been working on by myself for a while. It's a VR Action Shooter that makes you feel like Neo from the matrix.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nA mysterious group of rogues calling themselves STAR have kidnapped you. In this VR shooter you will right the wrongs of the \"evil\" Space Trading Association as you are tasked/forced into suicidal missions.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nA short concise adventure and a first glimpse into the STA Universe.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nDodge bullets and use an arsenal of weapons including a two handed assault rifle and a grenade launcher to dispense justice on those your master determines to be evil.",
